&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO WE ARE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Teague is an independent design consultancy that combines technology expertise with a deep understanding of human behavior to design what’s next for companies in automotive, commercial aviation, smart cities and infrastructure, advanced mobility, technology, space, and defense. On any given day, we might be prototyping a new space station, designing cutting-edge technology, or traveling around the world conducting research. We are approaching our one hundredth anniversary and are proudly employee-owned. Our culture fosters collaboration, accountability, and stability - because when we succeed,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;we all win&lt;/strong&gt;. Come be a part of something bigger than just a job - build your career with an employee-owned company that invests in you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;The Passenger Experience Research Center (PERC) Administrator plays a vital role in ensuring the smooth operation of the PERC facility and the successful execution of passenger experience surveys. This position supports an interactive exhibition in a museum setting. The PERC Administrator will use visitor engagement, facility management, and data collection to support Boeing&#39;s research initiatives. This is a temporary position from&lt;strong&gt; late July through all of August&lt;/strong&gt;, with hours ranging from part-time to full-time depending on availability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO YOU ARE: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You are a professional, organized, and customer-focused individual with at least one year of experience in customer service, hospitality, or administrative roles. You possess strong communication skills, excel in multitasking, and demonstrate proficiency in Microsoft Office programs like Word, Excel, and PowerPoint. A proactive mindset, reliability, and the ability to engage effectively with visitors are key. Weekend availability is essential, and an interest in aviation or science would be a valuable bonus. You will play a crucial role in ensuring the smooth operation of the facility and supporting Boeing&#39;s research initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;OWNING&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Open and close the PERC facility for daily operations, maintaining cleanliness, preparing survey materials, and managing the Boeing survey research tablets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Notify the Future of Flight and Boeing Tours teams about the day&#39;s anticipated survey schedule.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;At closing, shut down all systems, clean the facility, and reset for the next day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Complete additional tasks as assigned to support PERC operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
